*
*  Definition:
*  ===========
*
*       SUBROUTINE SPBEQU( UPLO, N, KD, AB, LDAB, S, SCOND, AMAX, INFO )
*
*       .. Scalar Arguments ..
*       CHARACTER          UPLO
*       INTEGER            INFO, KD, LDAB, N
*       REAL               AMAX, SCOND
*       ..
*       .. Array Arguments ..
*       REAL               AB( LDAB, * ), S( * )
*       ..
*
*
*> \par Purpose:
